node.text:
Giveaway day? Let’s do it. Three SIGNED copies of “Where Tomorrows Aren’t Promised” are up for grabs. 

Here’s how to enter:

Comment on this post, #WhereTomorrowsArentPromised and tag two friends who you think should hit the link in my bio to pick a copy up!

I’ll go through, pick three of you out, and get signed copies sent out next week!

node.text: Gone too soon. Talent aside, we were lucky to have someone as kind, genuine, and humble as you walking alongside us. I promise your legacy will carry on until we meet again one day brother. @bkbmg

node.text: It’s a special feeling to hold this book in my hands… Hit the link in my bio to pre-order #WhereTomorrowsArentPromised now, I promise it’s a story worth hearing. #STAYME7O

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Carmelo Anthony on August 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'GADL ANTHONY CARMELO D. WATKINS WITH C WHERE JONY TOMORROWS RE AREN'T 'S PROMISED MEMOIR OF SURVIVAL AND HOPE AND HOPE'.

node.text:
As an 18 year old if you told me I’d write a book one day I would’ve laughed at you. Where I come from, not many books are written about the lives we’ve lived. We are so focused on just making it to the next day. 

But today, the hard copies arrived and it’s a proud moment. I made it. 

Pre-order with the link in my bio.

#WhereTomorrowsArentPromised
